description:
Welcome to a new era of dance with Just Dance® 2023 Edition! Dance to 40 hot tracks, including:

""Dynamite"" by BTS, ""Boy With Luv"" by BTS Ft. Halsey, ""As It Was"" by Harry Styles, ""Therefore I Am"" by Billie Eilish, ""STAY"" by The Kid LAROI & Justin Bieber, ""Heat Waves"" by Glass Animals, ""Locked Out of Heaven"" by Bruno Mars, ""Physical"" by Dua Lipa, ""We Don't Talk About Bruno"" by Cast from Encanto, and more!
name: Just Dance® 2023 Edition Year 1
